      <title>Lodash源码解读</title>
      <link href="/2021/08/09/lodashread/"/>
      <url>/2021/08/09/lodashread/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="Lodash简介"><a href="#Lodash简介" class="headerlink" title="Lodash简介"></a>Lodash简介</h3><p>高性能、模块化的JS工具库</p><h3 id="数组方法"><a href="#数组方法" class="headerlink" title="数组方法"></a>数组方法</h3><h4 id="chunk"><a href="#chunk" class="headerlink" title="chunk"></a>chunk</h4><p>根据传入的size切分数组，返回一个二维数组结果</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment">// chunk(['a', 'b', 'c', 'd'], 2) -> [['a', 'b'], ['c', 'd']] 传入size刚好能被数组length整除时</span><span class="token comment">// chunk(['a', 'b', 'c', 'd'], 3) -> [['a', 'b', 'c'], ['c']]</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>源码</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-JavaScript" data-language="JavaScript"><code class="language-JavaScript">function chunk(array, size&#x3D;1) &#123;    size &#x3D; Math.max(toInteger(size), 0) &#x2F;&#x2F; 强转为整数    const length &#x3D; array &#x3D;&#x3D; null ? 0 : array.length &#x2F;&#x2F; 判断传入数组是否为null值    if (!length || size &lt; 1) &#123;        return [] &#x2F;&#x2F; 当传入的数组为空或者需要划分的size不大于一时返回[]    &#125;    let index &#x3D; 0    let resIndex &#x3D; 0    const result &#x3D; new Array(Math.ceil(length &#x2F; size)) &#x2F;&#x2F; 创建一个长度为划分过后大小的数组    while (index &lt; length) &#123;        result[resIndex++] &#x3D; slice(array, index, (index +&#x3D; size)) &#x2F;&#x2F; slice函数根据索引切割数组(lodash中的slice函数用于正确返回，代替了原本的Array的cancat函数)    &#125;)&#125;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="compact"><a href="#compact" class="headerlink" title="compact"></a>compact</h4><p>传入一个数组，返回一个过滤掉false、null、0、””、undefined、NaN的新数组</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token function">compact</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token boolean">false</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">0</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">''</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">3</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>源码</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">compact</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">array</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    <span class="token keyword">let</span> resIndex <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token number">0</span>    <span class="token keyword">const</span> result <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>array <span class="token operator">==</span> <span class="token keyword">null</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="token comment">// 判断array为null时</span>        <span class="token keyword">return</span> result    <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>    <span class="token keyword">for</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">const</span> value <span class="token keyword">of</span> array<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>        <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>value<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="token comment">// 过滤</span>            result<span class="token punctuation">[</span>resIndex<span class="token operator">++</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> value        <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>    <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> result<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><!-- #### concat --><h4 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h4><h4 id="difference"><a href="#difference" class="headerlink" title="difference"></a>difference</h4><p>传入多个数组，第一个作为标准，把第一个数组存在而后续数组不存在的值作为新数组的元素。</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment">// difference([3,2,1], [3,5]) -> [2,1]</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>源码</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment">/** * 函数解释： * isArrayLikeObject：检查传入的value是否是可转为数组或者是数组 * baseDifference：difference方法没有实现多个数组 * baseFlatten：flatten展开数组函数的没有实现限制条件的方法 **/</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">difference</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">array<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">...</span>value</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="token comment">// 传入数组，然后将除了第一个数组外的值展开到一个数组</span>    <span class="token comment">/**     * 首先判断传入的array是否是数组形式或可转为数组，     * 若为true，则使用baseDifference将array和value进行difference，     * 若false，返回true     **/</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">isArrayLikeObject</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>array<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">?</span> <span class="token function">baseDifference</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>array<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token function">baseFlatten</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>values<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> isArrayLikeObject<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="differenceBy-array-values-iteratee"><a href="#differenceBy-array-values-iteratee" class="headerlink" title="differenceBy(array, values, iteratee)"></a>differenceBy(array, values, iteratee)</h4><p>类似于difference函数，但是它多接收一个iteratee(迭代器)，使用迭代器分别迭代array和values，把迭代过后的值作为比较用的值。并且这个方法的返回值是一个新数组</p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment">// differenceBy([2.1, 1.2], [2.3, 3.4], Math.floor) -> [1.2]</span><span class="token function">differenceBy</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token string">'x'</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token string">'x'</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token string">'x'</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token string">'x'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span><span class="token string">'x'</span><span class="token operator">:</span> <span class="token number">2</span><span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>源码</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-javascript" data-language="javascript"><code class="language-javascript"><span class="token comment">/** * 函数解释： * last：获取数组的最后一个元素 **/</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token function">differenceBy</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">array<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token operator">...</span>values</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span>    <span class="token keyword">let</span> iteratee <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">last</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>values<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">// 获取迭代器</span>    <span class="token keyword">if</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token function">isArrayLikeObject</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>iteratee<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">&#123;</span> <span class="token comment">// 判断迭代器是否是数组形状或者Object</span>        iteratee <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">undefined</span>    <span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span>    <span class="token comment">/**     * 首先判断传入的array是否是数组形状，     * 若为true，使用baseDifference函数返回     * 若为false，返回[]     **/</span>    <span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">isArrayLike</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>array<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">?</span> <span class="token function">baseDifference</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>array<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token function">baseFlatten</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>values<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> isArrayLikeObject<span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> iteratee<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">:</span> 【<span class="token punctuation">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h4 id="differenceWith-array-values-comparator"><a href="#differenceWith-array-values-comparator" class="headerlink" title="differenceWith(array, values, comparator)"></a>differenceWith(array, values, comparator)</h4><p>依旧是类似与difference的一个方法，但是多接收一个comparator(比较器)的函数</p>]]></content>
      
      
